### Issue a certification (admin only, attempt must be GRADED and passed)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/certifications
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "quizAttemptId": "{{attemptId}}",
  "issuerName": "Dr. Ahmad bin Ismail",
  "issuerTitle": "Director, Sarawak Forestry Corporation",
  "companyName": "Sarawak Forestry Corporation",
  "expiryDate": "2028-04-16T00:00:00.000Z"
}

###

### List certifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/certifications
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Get a pre-signed download URL (S3 call skipped in testing)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/certifications/{{certId}}/download
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Public verify a certificate (no auth required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/certifications/verify/{{certId}}
